reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars The rubber end is too soft and tore immediately.
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this universal dishwasher drain hose and installed it in my daughter's town home. All seemed to be well until her roommate discovered water stains on the ceiling in the room below the kitchen. Upon further investigation we found that where the clamp attached the rubber end of this universal dishwasher drain hose to the garbage disposal had torn at the clamp. The rubber is too thin and too soft. We were very unhappy and it resulted in a water leak and stain. Too bad for us. I found an manufacturers original drain hose for nearly the same price and had to replace the one I got on Amazon. We do not recommend this Universal drain hose at all.
